name: Anita Dongre
text: We are in this together and we will come out on the other side stronger. Thank you for all you have done for House of Anita Dongre. We shall overcome. (5/5)

name: Anita Dongre
text: For all our direct employees, in addition to paid leaves, we already have a medical insurance in place that covers them and their family members. In case of an additional emergency, this fund will be extended to them as well. (4/5)

name: Anita Dongre
text: It is for this reason that the #AnitaDongeFoundation has decided to set up a dedicated fund to support any medical treatments arising during these times. The fund will cover our smaller vendors, self-employed artisans & partners who do not have medical insurance or coverage.(3/5)

name: Anita Dongre
text: Among the people who are likely to be most affected by these changes are the small vendors and self-employed artisans who contribute to the work you love and admire. We recognise that not many of them will have resources available to cover a potential medical emergency. (2/5)

name: Anita Dongre
text: A lot has changed in the last few days. Our interactions. Our work. Our relationships. All faced drastic upheavals. Upheavals that can include unforeseen medical emergencies in the coming days. (1/5)
